| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5951 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9405217a-48c8-5e19-9cd8-d48896271bb0"
